420
00:42:58,060 --> 00:43:01,390
我最喜欢你的一点就是…
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}...one of the things I've always liked about you...

421
00:43:01,460 --> 00:43:03,450
小乖…
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}...Kiddo...

422
00:43:04,730 --> 00:43:07,890
你看起来比实际的年龄更聪明
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}...is you appear wise beyond your years.

423
00:43:11,570 --> 00:43:16,200
让我给你这聪明人一点忠告:
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}So, allow me to impart a word to the wise:

424
00:43:16,270 --> 00:43:17,900
无论如何…
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Whatever...

425
00:43:17,980 --> 00:43:21,940
不管白眉说什么，你都得服从
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}...whatever Pai Mei says, obey.

426
00:43:23,350 --> 00:43:28,480
即使你短暂地露出些许不敬的眼神
他立刻把你眼珠子挖出来
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}If you flash him, even for an instant, a defiant eye, he'll pluck it out.

427
00:43:29,220 --> 00:43:33,780
如果你的美式骄傲触怒了他…
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}And if you throw any American sass his way...

428
00:43:33,860 --> 00:43:37,060
他会把你脊椎
和脖子像小树枝一般地劈断
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}...he'll snap your back and your neck like they were twigs.

429
00:43:40,500 --> 00:43:43,300
那你就成为一个故事了
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}And that will be the story of you.

430
00:44:03,590 --> 00:44:06,150
他答应收你为徒了
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}He'll accept you as his student.

431
00:44:06,220 --> 00:44:08,320
- 你怎么啦？
- 没事儿
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}- What happened to you? - Nothin'.

432
00:44:08,390 --> 00:44:11,560
- 和他动手了？
- 朋友间过个招罢了
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}- Get in a fight? - Friendly contest.

433
00:44:11,630 --> 00:44:13,060
他怎么会答应收我的？
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Why did he accept me?

434
00:44:13,130 --> 00:44:17,400
因为他已经很老很老了
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Because he's a very, very, very old man.

435
00:44:17,470 --> 00:44:20,700
和其他老不死的王八蛋一样…
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}And like all rotten bastards...

436
00:44:20,770 --> 00:44:25,940
他愈老就愈寂寞.
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}...when they become old, they get lonely.

437
00:44:26,010 --> 00:44:28,980
年纪改不了他的脾气
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Which has no effect on their dispositions,

438
00:44:29,050 --> 00:44:33,780
但也让他学到了，有个伴儿的重要
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}but it does teach them the value of company.

439
00:44:33,850 --> 00:44:36,340
哇赛
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Whew. Oh.

440
00:44:36,420 --> 00:44:41,320
光是瞧这些台阶，我腿就软了
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Just seein' those steps again makes me ache.

441
00:44:41,960 --> 00:44:47,230
以后你挑着水桶上上下下的
可有你乐的啦
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}You're gonna have a lot of fun carrying buckets of water up and down that fucker.

442
00:44:51,740 --> 00:44:53,800
我何时能再见到你？
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}When will I see you again?

443
00:44:53,870 --> 00:44:57,360
就像我最喜欢的70年代
一首黑人灵歌的歌名
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}That's the title of my favorite soul song of the seventies.

444
00:44:57,440 --> 00:44:59,240
- 啥？
- 没什么
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}- What? - Nothin'.

445
00:44:59,310 --> 00:45:01,780
等他说你可以出师时
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}When he tells me you're done.

446
00:45:02,850 --> 00:45:04,540
你想会是何时？
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}When do you think that might be?

447
00:45:04,620 --> 00:45:07,550
亲爱的，那全看你自己了
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}That, my dearest, depends entirely on you.

448
00:45:07,620 --> 00:45:11,250
记住，切勿讥讽，切勿顶撞
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Now remember, no sarcasm, no backtalk.

449
00:45:11,320 --> 00:45:13,620
起码头一两年里
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}At least not for the first year or so.

450
00:45:13,690 --> 00:45:16,890
你得给他时间来
慢慢让你进入状况
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}You're gonna have to let him warm up to you.

451
00:45:16,960 --> 00:45:20,800
他讨厌白人，藐视美国人
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}He hates Caucasians, despises Americans,

452
00:45:20,870 --> 00:45:23,660
更不喜欢女人
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}and has nothing but contempt for women.

453
00:45:26,040 --> 00:45:29,440
所以像你这种情行
得多花点儿时间了
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}So in your case... it might take a little while.

454
00:45:30,440 --> 00:45:33,140
再见啦
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}- Adios.

455
00:47:12,480 --> 00:47:13,570
师父…
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Master...

456
00:47:15,410 --> 00:47:17,110
你的汉语好差
我一个字也听不懂
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Your Mandarin is lousy.

457
00:47:17,110 --> 00:47:21,110
我一个字也听不懂
而且好刺耳！
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}It causes my ears discomfort. You bray like an ass!

458
00:47:21,920 --> 00:47:24,050
我没要你说话，你就别说
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}You are not to speak unless spoken to.

459
00:47:24,960 --> 00:47:28,550
你的汉语好呢
还是你的广东话好？
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Is it too much to hope -- you understand Cantonese?

460
00:47:32,300 --> 00:47:33,700
我的日语很好…
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}I speak Japanese very well--

461
00:47:33,770 --> 00:47:37,060
我没问你日本话
也没问你蒙古话
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}I didn't ask if you speak Japanese --

462
00:47:37,140 --> 00:47:39,300
我问你会不会说广东话？
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}I asked if you understand Cantonese?

463
00:47:40,840 --> 00:47:41,830
一点点
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}A little.

464
00:47:42,510 --> 00:47:47,100
你是来学武的，不是学讲话
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}You are here to learn the mysteries of Kung Fu, not linguistics.

465
00:47:47,510 --> 00:47:49,610
如果你不懂汉语
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}If you can't understand me --

466
00:47:49,680 --> 00:47:51,170
就像狗一样
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}I will communicate with you like I would a dog.

467
00:47:51,480 --> 00:47:54,970
我会斥喝你，命令你，用棍打你！
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}When I yell, when I point, when I beat you with my stick!

468
00:48:01,060 --> 00:48:02,920
你的师父是不是比尔？
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Bill is your master, is he not?

469
00:48:04,830 --> 00:48:06,320
是的
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Yes, he is.

470
00:48:08,670 --> 00:48:12,470
你师傅说过你曾经学过武术
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Your master tells me -- you're not entirely unschooled.

471
00:48:13,400 --> 00:48:14,770
你学过些什么？
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}What training do you possess?

472
00:48:15,670 --> 00:48:18,270
我精通虎鹤拳
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}I am proficient in Tiger-Crane Style,

473
00:48:18,340 --> 00:48:22,340
更精通日本武士道剑术
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}and I am more than proficient in the exquisite art of the Samurai sword.

474
00:48:23,710 --> 00:48:26,210
哼～日本剑道
开什么玩笑！
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}The exquisite art of the Samurai sword. Don't make me laugh!

475
00:48:26,750 --> 00:48:31,350
你所谓的剑道不值个屁
你就更加笨
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Your so-called exquisite art, is only fit for --

476
00:48:31,690 --> 00:48:33,280
你居然敢正视我
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Japanese fat heads!

477
00:48:38,430 --> 00:48:43,560
看你的脾气都可以学武
你觉得本道的功夫跟你比如何？
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Your anger amuses me. Do you believe you are my match?

478
00:48:44,100 --> 00:48:44,690
不知
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}No.

479
00:48:45,540 --> 00:48:47,500
你知道本道会杀人吗？
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Are you aware I kill at will?

480
00:48:48,170 --> 00:48:49,230
知道
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Yes.

481
00:48:49,740 --> 00:48:51,140
那么你是想死？
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Is it your wish to die?

482
00:48:51,540 --> 00:48:51,910
不
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}No.

483
00:48:54,080 --> 00:48:55,850
傻瓜
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Then you must be stupid...

484
00:48:55,850 --> 00:48:57,450
真是傻瓜
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Then you must be stupid...so stupid.

485
00:48:57,520 --> 00:49:01,250
本道好想看看你有多傻
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Rise, and let me look at your ridiculous face.

486
00:49:01,750 --> 00:49:02,910
起身
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Rise.

487
00:49:07,460 --> 00:49:13,860
亏你还学过虎鹤拳
刚才走了一百来台阶就在喘了
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}So my pathetic friend... Is there anything that you can do well?

488
00:49:13,930 --> 00:49:15,870
我看你不单是傻
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}What's the matter?

489
00:49:16,300 --> 00:49:18,230
身体也很虚啊
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Cat got your tongue?

490
00:49:19,700 --> 00:49:22,670
喔，对了，你会说日本话
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}-- Oh yes, you speak Japanese.

491
00:49:23,310 --> 00:49:24,740
我最恨日本人！
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}I despise the Goddamn Japs!

492
00:49:27,780 --> 00:49:29,510
去兵器架那边
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Go to that rack.

493
00:49:37,820 --> 00:49:38,790
拔那把剑
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Remove the sword.

494
00:50:05,120 --> 00:50:06,910
我要看下你的武功有多深
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Let's see how good you really are.

495
00:50:07,790 --> 00:50:09,410
出招.
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}If...

496
00:50:10,090 --> 00:50:11,780
如果我输给你的话
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}...you land a single blow,

497
00:50:13,520 --> 00:50:15,250
我干脆拜你为师
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}I'll bow down and call you master.

498
00:50:29,510 --> 00:50:31,910
你看到我的功夫了吧
试我的脚法
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}From here you can get an excellent view of my foot.

499
00:50:37,150 --> 00:50:40,480
你的剑术…只是一般入门的水平
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Your swordsmanship -- is amateur at best.

500
00:50:54,630 --> 00:50:57,770
残废也比你强
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Your so-called kung-fu -- is really -- quite pathetic.

501
00:50:57,830 --> 00:50:58,970
再来啊！

502
00:50:59,630 --> 00:51:00,970
废物

503
00:51:02,810 --> 00:51:06,610
我已经给你机会显示一下你的武功
我看到了
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}I asked you to demonstrate -- what you know -- and you did...

504
00:51:07,310 --> 00:51:08,510
你一点都不会
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Not a goddamn thing!

505
00:51:09,580 --> 00:51:13,210
现在我要你以虎鹤拳
和我的鹰爪拳比试一下
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Let's see your Tiger Crane -- match my Eagle's Claw.

506
00:52:10,370 --> 00:52:12,340
你和其他美国女人一样
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Like all Yankee women...

507
00:52:12,410 --> 00:52:15,900
只知道在餐馆点菜，花男人的钱
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}...all you can do is order in restaurants and spend a man's money.

508
00:52:17,050 --> 00:52:18,680
痛吗？ 我问你呢？
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Excruciating -- isn't it?

509
00:52:18,750 --> 00:52:20,010
痛！
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Yes!

510
00:52:21,590 --> 00:52:22,920
你相不相信我…
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}If it was my wish...

511
00:52:23,420 --> 00:52:24,750
随时能砍下你的手臂
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}...I could chop your arm off.

512
00:52:24,820 --> 00:52:26,080
不要！
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}No, please don't!

513
00:52:27,560 --> 00:52:29,860
你相不相信我想怎样就怎样
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}It's my arm now. I can do what I please.

514
00:52:30,490 --> 00:52:32,720
如果你不想我砍你的手…动手！
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}If you can stop me -- I suggest you try.

515
00:52:34,970 --> 00:52:35,950
我不行
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}I can't.

516
00:52:37,130 --> 00:52:38,360
打不过吧
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Because you're helpless?

517
00:52:39,240 --> 00:52:40,130
对
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Yes.

518
00:52:42,770 --> 00:52:44,870
你以前试过这种滋味吗？
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Have you ever felt this before?

519
00:52:45,280 --> 00:52:46,070
没有
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}No.

520
00:52:46,440 --> 00:52:49,740
你的功夫和我比，简直是班门弄斧
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Compared to me -- you're as helpless as a worm fighting an eagle?

521
00:52:50,750 --> 00:52:51,940
是的！！！
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}YES!!!

522
00:52:54,150 --> 00:52:54,880
现在开始
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}THAT'S THE BEGlNNlNG!

523
00:53:00,660 --> 00:53:03,290
你想不想学
我刚才和你打的这套拳？
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Is it your wish to possess this kind of power?

524
00:53:06,000 --> 00:53:07,590
想！
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Yes!

525
00:53:09,170 --> 00:53:10,990
从明天开始你要练武
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Your training will begin -- tomorrow.

526
00:53:11,790 --> 00:53:12,930
记住

527
00:53:20,710 --> 00:53:22,080
你的手臂属于我…
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Since your arm now belongs to me...

528
00:53:22,980 --> 00:53:24,980
我会将它练得结实
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}...I want it strong.

529
00:53:25,850 --> 00:53:27,250
你能不能做到像我这样？
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Can you do that?

530
00:53:28,950 --> 00:53:30,610
可以，不过还差你一节
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}I can, but not that close.

531
00:53:30,790 --> 00:53:32,090
那就是不行了！
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Then you can't do it.

532
00:53:33,320 --> 00:53:37,090
如果敌人离你的身体只有三寸…
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}What if your enemy -- is three inches in front of you...

533
00:53:38,160 --> 00:53:39,420
你怎么对付他？
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}...What do you do then...

534
00:53:40,560 --> 00:53:41,660
抱头鼠窜…
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}...Curl into a ball...

535
00:53:43,330 --> 00:53:44,600
还是用拳打穿他？
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}...or do you put your FlST through him?

536
00:53:46,170 --> 00:53:46,930
现在开始
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Now begin.

537
00:54:19,170 --> 00:54:20,690
练拳头不应该是你怕木头
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}It's the wood that should fear your hand --

538
00:54:20,770 --> 00:54:23,240
应该是木头怕你
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}-- not the other way around.

539
00:54:24,040 --> 00:54:28,310
你之所以打不穿木头
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}No wonder you can't do it -- you acquiesce to defeat --

540
00:54:28,380 --> 00:54:29,810
是因为你用手之前已经认输了
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}-- before you even begin.

541
00:56:18,290 --> 00:56:20,520
如果你像狗一样吃东西
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}If you want to eat like a dog...

542
00:56:21,790 --> 00:56:23,780
我就让你像狗一样住外面
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}You can live and sleep outside like a dog.

543
00:56:26,300 --> 00:56:28,200
如果你想像人一样的话
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}If you want to live and sleep like a human...

544
00:56:29,800 --> 00:56:31,290
把筷子拿起来
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}...pick up those sticks.

545
01:00:02,210 --> 01:00:05,840
快，你混蛋
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Come on, you bitch.

546
01:00:46,820 --> 01:00:49,450
好，白眉
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}OK, Pai Mei.

547
01:00:51,660 --> 01:00:53,990
我来了
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Here I come.

548
01:03:02,630 --> 01:03:06,760
请给我一杯水？
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}May I have a glass of water, please?

549
01:03:08,430 --> 01:03:10,110
第九章

550
01:03:10,110 --> 01:03:12,760
第九章：艾儿和我

551
01:05:43,950 --> 01:05:47,390
- 原来那就是德州式葬礼？
- 对
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}-Sothat's a Texas funeral? - Yep.

552
01:05:48,990 --> 01:05:51,290
我不得不承认你还真行，巴德
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}I have to give it to ya, Budd.

553
01:05:51,360 --> 01:05:54,450
这种死法还真凄惨
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}That's a pretty fucked up way to die.

554
01:05:54,530 --> 01:05:56,960
她墓碑上是什么名字？
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}What's the name on the grave she's buried under?

555
01:05:57,830 --> 01:05:59,630
宝…
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Paula...

556
01:06:01,200 --> 01:06:03,230
休兹
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}...Schultz.

557
01:06:08,570 --> 01:06:09,970
能看看那把刀吗？
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Can I look at the sword?

558
01:06:10,040 --> 01:06:13,600
我的钱就在那红箱子里，对吧？
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}That's my money right there in that red bag, isn't it?

559
01:06:13,680 --> 01:06:16,380
没错
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}It sure is.

560
01:06:16,450 --> 01:06:18,850
那好，刀是你的啦
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Well then, it's your sword now.

561
01:06:35,140 --> 01:06:38,070
那么，这就是那把半藏的刀咯！
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}(blender whirring)

562
01:06:38,140 --> 01:06:40,070
你刚说啥？
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}What's that you said?

563
01:06:40,140 --> 01:06:42,540
这就是服部半藏铸的刀？
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}So this is a Hattori Hanzo sword?

564
01:06:42,610 --> 01:06:44,940
没错，就是半藏的刀
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}That's a Hanzo sword, all right.

565
01:06:45,010 --> 01:06:47,780
比尔告诉我
你曾经也有一把他的刀
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Bill tells me you once had one of these of your own.

566
01:06:49,350 --> 01:06:51,340
对，曾经
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Yeah, once.

