{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}...is a strip that says I'm pregnant.

1046
01:51:47,240 --> 01:51:48,400
鬼扯！
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Bullshit.

1047
01:51:49,680 --> 01:51:53,340
换做别时，你一定没错
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Any other time you'd be 100 percent right.

1048
01:51:53,420 --> 01:51:56,280
但这次…
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}This time...

1049
01:51:56,350 --> 01:51:58,380
你完全错了
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}...you're 100 percent wrong.

1050
01:52:00,920 --> 01:52:04,520
我是世上能要人命的女人…
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}I'm the deadliest woman in the world.

1051
01:52:04,590 --> 01:52:06,790
但现在…
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}But right now...

1052
01:52:06,860 --> 01:52:09,230
有了孩子我却怕了
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}...I'm just scared shitless for my baby.

1053
01:52:10,100 --> 01:52:12,090
求你！
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Please.

1054
01:52:13,200 --> 01:52:15,600
看一下验孕器
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Just look at the strip.

1055
01:52:17,670 --> 01:52:19,400
求你！
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Please.

1056
01:52:20,710 --> 01:52:25,440
待在原地别动
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Stay where you are and don't move.

1057
01:52:42,630 --> 01:52:45,000
妈的，我不懂这表示啥？
