1061
01:53:05,620 --> 01:53:07,280
蓝色代表怀孕
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Blue means pregnant.

1062
01:53:08,090 --> 01:53:10,080
我自己会读，不用你多事
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}I'll read it myself, thank you.

1063
01:53:16,970 --> 01:53:19,900
哦，好
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Oh, OK.

1064
01:53:19,970 --> 01:53:22,200
好吧，如果我相信你
下面该怎么做？
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Say I were to believe you. What then?

1065
01:53:22,270 --> 01:53:24,900
你回家吧
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Just go home.

1066
01:53:26,010 --> 01:53:28,100
我也回家
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}I'll do the same.

1067
01:53:47,700 --> 01:53:49,290
恭喜你！
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Congratulations.

1068
01:53:52,970 --> 01:53:55,770
在验孕器变蓝色前…
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Before that strip turned blue...

1069
01:53:55,840 --> 01:53:59,280
我是个女人，我是你的女人
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}...I was a woman, I was your woman.

1070
01:53:59,340 --> 01:54:02,900
我是你的杀手…为你而杀
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}I was a killer who killed for you.

1071
01:54:02,980 --> 01:54:06,070
在验孕器变成蓝色前
我愿意以从摩托车上…
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Before that strip turned blue, I would've jumped a motorcycle

1072
01:54:06,150 --> 01:54:09,140
跳到高速飞驰的火车上
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}onto a speeding train.

1073
01:54:09,220 --> 01:54:11,210
为了你
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}For you.

1074
01:54:12,520 --> 01:54:15,890
一但验孕器变蓝色以后…
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}But once that strip turned blue...

1075
01:54:15,960 --> 01:54:19,450
我再也无法做那些事了
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}...I could no longer do any of those things.

1076
01:54:19,530 --> 01:54:22,000
再也不能了
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Not anymore.

1077
01:54:22,070 --> 01:54:24,630
因为我要做妈妈了
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Because I was gonna be a mother.

1078
01:54:27,740 --> 01:54:29,500
你能了解吗？
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Can you understand that?

1079
01:54:32,710 --> 01:54:35,300
能
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Yes.

1080
01:54:35,380 --> 01:54:37,540
但你为什么不…
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}But why didn't you...

1081
01:54:37,610 --> 01:54:40,780
