{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}...tell me then, instead of now?

1082
01:54:40,850 --> 01:54:43,150
你一旦知道，她就是你的了
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Once you knew, you'd claim her.

1083
01:54:43,220 --> 01:54:45,210
我不希望那样
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}And I didn't want that.

1084
01:54:45,960 --> 01:54:48,190
