{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}...she would've been born into a world she shouldn't have.

1090
01:55:07,240 --> 01:55:10,440
我必须作选择
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}I had to choose.

1091
01:55:10,510 --> 01:55:12,500
