{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}I chose her.

1092
01:55:15,090 --> 01:55:17,880
你知道…如果5年前
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}You know, five years ago,

1093
01:55:17,950 --> 01:55:22,820
要我列出绝不可能发生事情的清单
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}if I had to make a list of impossible things that could never happen,

1094
01:55:22,890 --> 01:55:28,530
