{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}you performing a coup de grace on me by bustin' a cap in my crown...

1095
01:55:30,930 --> 01:55:33,600
绝对会排在第一位
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}...would've been right at the top of the list.

1096
01:55:35,270 --> 01:55:37,300
但是我错了，不是吗？
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}I'd have been wrong, wouldn't l?

1097
01:55:38,610 --> 01:55:40,540
对不起
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}I-I'm sorry.

1098
01:55:40,610 --> 01:55:42,740
那是个问我的问题吗？
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Was that a question?

1099
01:55:43,980 --> 01:55:49,910
如果说你认为那是不可能发生的事
这样说的话，你是错了
{\fnTahoma\fs12\b0}Of impossible things that could never happen - yes, in this instance, you would've been wrong.

1100
01:55:50,820 --> 01:55:51,880
